name: Alexander Akbashev
body:
### About me
Hi! As you can already understand, my name is Akbashev Alexander. I was born in tiny Russian town called [Satka](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Satka). After ~27 years and several stopovers I moved to Berlin, Germany. I'm interesting in software development, code quality, get things done and a lot of other stuff. 

### Opensource projects
+ [S3 Plugin for Jenkins](https://wiki.jenkins-ci.org/display/JENKINS/S3+Plugin)

Allows to publish and download artifacts from AWS S3 storage
+ [Groovy Event Listener Plugin for Jenkins](https://wiki.jenkins-ci.org/display/JENKINS/Groovy+Events+Listener+Plugin)

Executes groovy code before (or after) every build in Jenkins

+ Fluentd Plugin for Jenkins (work in progress)

Posts data to Fluentd agent

+ Parallel-gtest (work in progress)

Run tests based on Google Test Framework in parallel
